#: jinwu.core.ogip.OgipTimeSeriesBase.extract_gti:3 of
msgid ""
"Default implementation searches for an extension named 'GTI' (case-"
"insensitive) and, if present, returns a list of (START, STOP) pairs. "
"Readers should call this to populate event objects' GTI field."
msgstr ""
"默认实现在（大小写不敏感）名为 'GTI' 的扩展中搜索，若存在则返回 (START, STOP) 对列表。"
"读取器应调用此方法填充事例对象的 GTI 字段。"

